query:
SELECT r.id, r.questionId, q.questionKey, r.value, r.comment, r.responseId, r.updatedAt 
FROM responses r
JOIN questions q ON r.questionId = q.id
WHERE r.partnerQuestionnaireId = 1
ORDER BY r.updatedAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
